S.FORM: == Qus == u sulit nu Hulam: 和平部落 i Taoyuan a kuwan nu Kalinku ku niyazu' nu Qus. u kasalumaluma' nu Qus sa, 14 ku luma'. kumud nu kasabinawlan sa, 47 ku tademawan. kasabinawlan nu Ingcumin sa, 40 ku tademaw, pakalatu 85%. u zuma sa, cay ku Ingcumin, 7 ku tademaw, pakalatu 15%. u kasabinacadan, Tayal 79%, Amis 4%, Paiwan 2%. Qus u sulit nu Hulam: 庫志部落 i Taoyuan a kuwan nu Kalinku ku niyazu' nu Qus. u kasalumaluma' nu Qus sa, 75 ku luma'. kumud nu kasabinawlan sa, 168 ku tademawan. kasabinawlan nu Ingcumin sa, 146 ku tademaw, pakalatu 87%. u zuma sa, cay ku Ingcumin, 22 ku tademaw, pakalatu 13%. u kasabinacadan, Tayal 81%, Amis 2%, zumazuma 4%.

== Qos == o solit no Holam: 和平部落 i Taoyoan a kowan no Kalinko ko niyazo' no Qos. o kasalomaloma' no Qos sa, 14 ko loma'. komod no kasabinawlan sa, 47 ko tademawan. kasabinawlan no Ingcomin sa, 40 ko tademaw, pakalato 85%. o zoma sa, cay ko Ingcomin, 7 ko tademaw, pakalato 15%. o kasabinacadan, Tayal 79%, Amis 4%, Paiwan 2%. Qos o solit no Holam: 庫志部落 i Taoyoan a kowan no Kalinko ko niyazo' no Qos. o kasalomaloma' no Qos sa, 75 ko loma'. komod no kasabinawlan sa, 168 ko tademawan. kasabinawlan no Ingcomin sa, 146 ko tademaw, pakalato 87%. o zoma sa, cay ko Ingcomin, 22 ko tademaw, pakalato 13%. o kasabinacadan, Tayal 81%, Amis 2%, zomazoma 4%.
